Mojo::Log::More - Mojo::Log with More details

This module is a small wrapper around Mojo::Log which allows you to log
caller() information with your log messages automatically. You do not need
to use big logging systems like Log::Dispatch or Log::Log4perl
to get this feature anymore.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Mojo::Log::More

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Mojo-Log-More

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Mojo-Log-More

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Mojo-Log-More

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Mojo-Log-More/


